'''喬·科特尼'''（Joe Courtney ；{{bd|1953年|4月6日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物。自2007年開始，他是康涅狄格州第2選舉區選出的美國眾議院議員<ref>{{cite news |author= Jennifer Medina |title= Democrat Wins House Seat After Recount in Connecticut |newspaper= New York Times |date= November 16, 2006 |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/16/nyregion/16recount.html |accessdate= 2016-01-04 |archive-date= 2021-01-04 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210104065332/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/11/16/nyregion/16recount.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。他的黨籍是[[民主黨_(美國)|民主黨]]。科特尼畢業於[[塔夫茨大學|塔夫茨大學]]。他已經結婚並且有兩個孩子。

2021年，他主持了[[康涅狄格号核动力潜艇撞击事件|康涅狄格号核动力潜艇撞击事件]]的听证会<ref>{{Cite web|title=Investigation Concludes USS Connecticut Grounded on Uncharted Seamount in South China Sea|url=https://news.usni.org/2021/11/01/investigation-concludes-uss-connecticut-grounded-on-uncharted-sea-mount-in-south-china-sea|date=2021-11-01|publisher={{tsl|en|United States Naval Institute|美国海军学会}}|access-date=2021-11-05|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120133717/https://news.usni.org/2021/11/01/investigation-concludes-uss-connecticut-grounded-on-uncharted-sea-mount-in-south-china-sea|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

